{"tid":608703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都有啲特殊既習慣/癖好令自已易啲熟睡","createTime":"2018-03-28T11:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T11:48:44.000Z","uid":89402,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6c34ef7056267ac0f219588e493ec3c0620e91","tid":608703,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"如題 我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.細細個時要阿媽一路摸我個頭一路氹我訓教<br />\n真係好快訓著<br />\n<br />\n2.細個好撚驚鬼 又細膽<br />\n所以如果自已一個係房訓既話就一定要開住收音機<br />\n有人講嘢有啲聲覺得好安全 易啲訓著<br />\n<br />\n3.一定要攬住嘢訓教<br />\n<br />\n4.側睡訓個時好撚中意用手指掃自已條眉毛<br />\n掃掃下就會訓著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.沖完涼 隻腳好似特別滑<br />\n所以訓個時會係咁用腳磨張被 <br />\n覺得張被特別舒服特別軟 要磨撚到訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後諗撚返起以前個ex<br />\n同佢訓教個時都有個癖好<br />\n最中意我一路攬住佢訓一路揸佢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸撚到佢訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返起都好撚正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講講下開始有啲眼訓<br />\n唔講咁多 即刻訓教！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7324f1e25ca2807144abde76943ec23bfd97fb38","tid":608703,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"扑完野秒訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5044f1059829ced4ac0c12e588da03936202e76","tid":608703,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"拎隻貓黎聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue